00:38.388 --> 00:39.955
You still hittin' the sauce?

00:39.990 --> 00:42.524
Yeah, but, I mean,
I got it under control.

00:42.559 --> 00:43.525
Uh-huh.

00:43.560 --> 00:44.793
Falling off the wagon

00:44.827 --> 00:48.030
is typically followed
by a bit of a bender.

00:48.064 --> 00:51.068
I mean, it usually works
itself out in a week or three.

00:51.103 --> 00:53.271
Ohh.

00:53.305 --> 00:55.674
I'm not worried.

00:55.708 --> 00:57.309
I'm glad to hear that.

00:57.343 --> 00:59.311
I'm sorry, Hank.

00:59.345 --> 01:01.680
Okay?
They'll get over it.

01:01.714 --> 01:03.248
- Eventually.
- Yeah.

01:03.282 --> 01:04.649
Yeah, in a week or three,

01:04.684 --> 01:06.385
but that's the thing about this thing.

01:06.420 --> 01:08.254
- Hmm.
- There's nothing to get over.

01:08.288 --> 01:10.390
- Hey--
- I didn't actually do anything.

01:10.424 --> 01:12.392
Uh, you--you're
preaching to the choir, honey.

01:12.427 --> 01:14.361
Okay?
I wouldn't give two fucks

01:14.396 --> 01:16.163
if you had done it the way
they think you've done it.

01:16.198 --> 01:17.231
But I didn't done it.

01:17.266 --> 01:19.735
Okay. I get it.

01:21.604 --> 01:22.972
Man, you know I'd never tell, right?

01:23.006 --> 01:25.508
That shit would be between
you, me, and the wall.

01:25.543 --> 01:26.910
I'd take a fuckin' blood oath.

01:26.944 --> 01:29.113
- Nothing actually happened.
- Okay.

01:29.147 --> 01:30.248
So there's nothing to tell you.

01:30.282 --> 01:32.050
- I believe you.
- It's due today, so...

01:32.085 --> 01:35.221
Both: I'm sorry, baby.

01:35.255 --> 01:37.390
Come in.
I'll make you some breakfast.

01:37.424 --> 01:39.092
Ooh, yummy--that sounds good.
I could eat.

01:39.126 --> 01:40.761
Can you tell him
I'm not talking to him?

01:40.795 --> 01:42.896
- She's not talking to him.
- What?

01:42.930 --> 01:44.798
Well, that's a fine
how-do-you-do-do.

01:44.832 --> 01:46.433
You'll forgive him, but not me?

01:46.467 --> 01:47.934
I'll work on her for you.

01:47.969 --> 01:49.437
One day at a time, Batesy.

01:49.471 --> 01:52.640
[Cell phone chiming]

01:52.674 --> 01:55.276
Ah, hells to the no!

01:55.310 --> 01:56.644
Hank fuckin' Moody.
[Rap music in background]

01:56.678 --> 01:58.946
No more notes, Sam.
I can't take it.

01:58.980 --> 02:00.414
Just find another writer.

02:00.449 --> 02:02.450
I won't be offended.
I promise.

02:02.484 --> 02:03.817
It ain't about that movie shit, man.

02:03.852 --> 02:06.520
I need to see your ass now, though.

02:06.555 --> 02:08.823
- What about?
- Kali.

02:08.857 --> 02:11.360
What about Kali?

02:11.394 --> 02:12.661
Not over the phone, nigga.

02:12.696 --> 02:15.498
Just get your ass over
to my studio right now.

02:18.002 --> 02:19.803
- You hear me?
- Yeah. I'm coming.

02:19.837 --> 02:21.705
Or else my boys come get you,
nigga--your choice.

02:21.740 --> 02:23.307
No, no, no, no.
No, that--that's okay.

02:23.342 --> 02:25.043
Don't blow me off, Moody.
I'm serious, man.

02:25.077 --> 02:26.477
I'm on my way.

02:26.512 --> 02:27.979
All right, mo'fucker.

02:28.013 --> 02:29.414
[Phone beeps]

02:30.616 --> 02:33.585
[Upbeat music]

02:33.620 --> 02:43.594
