05:27.631 --> 05:28.798
I didn't come all the way here

05:28.832 --> 05:30.699
to write cheesy love songs.

05:30.733 --> 05:32.267
Sorry, that's my thing.

05:32.301 --> 05:33.635
I specialize in cheese--

05:33.669 --> 05:35.636
big, gooey globs of it.

05:35.671 --> 05:36.738
You're out of luck.

05:36.772 --> 05:39.307
Okay, I just want it to be...

05:39.341 --> 05:41.108
bittersweet and dark.

05:41.143 --> 05:45.846
Well, you are nothing
if not a semisweet piece of...

05:45.881 --> 05:47.114
Milk chocolate?

05:49.051 --> 05:50.952
You are cheesy.

05:50.986 --> 05:51.986
Yeah.

05:52.020 --> 05:54.188
Speaking of love
and whatnot, um--

05:54.223 --> 05:55.590
Oh, two whiskies, barkeep, please,

05:55.624 --> 05:56.658
and keep 'em coming.

05:56.692 --> 05:58.826
I think the samurai is deep in it.

05:58.861 --> 06:00.128
Wit' you.

06:00.162 --> 06:01.397
God, please.

06:01.431 --> 06:03.265
What the fuck does that guy
know about love?

06:03.299 --> 06:04.834
He's a spoiled man-child.

06:04.868 --> 06:07.736
He gets whatever he wants,
and he can't have me.

06:07.771 --> 06:09.638
He just wants to control his product.

06:09.673 --> 06:11.106
I don't think that's it.

06:11.141 --> 06:13.141
I-I think everybody's
got that special someone

06:13.175 --> 06:15.109
that gets under their skin
and doesn't go away.

06:15.144 --> 06:16.110
I think maybe you have

06:16.145 --> 06:18.079
that particular
fungal property for him.

06:18.113 --> 06:19.980
[Chuckles]

06:20.015 --> 06:22.449
All right,
so if somebody was asking me

06:22.484 --> 06:23.850
about a short story,

06:23.885 --> 06:26.920
I'd ask them,
"What are you trying to say?"

06:28.456 --> 06:29.489
I don't know.

06:29.524 --> 06:33.092
Um...

06:33.127 --> 06:34.995
I'd love to talk about

06:35.029 --> 06:38.465
coming to L.A.
for the first time.

06:38.499 --> 06:41.902
And the fact that you
tend to leave something

06:41.936 --> 06:43.604
or someone behind.

06:43.638 --> 06:45.339
All right.

06:45.373 --> 06:47.742
Now we're getting somewhere.
I can relate to that.

06:47.776 --> 06:52.013
I can remember that shit
as if it were fuckin' yesterday.

06:52.048 --> 06:53.382
[Car horn blares]

06:55.486 --> 06:57.187
So what do you think?

06:57.221 --> 06:58.655
I don't know, you know.

06:58.690 --> 07:00.057
I think we should keep looking.

07:00.091 --> 07:01.292
- Really?
- Yeah.

07:01.326 --> 07:02.994
Oh, I got a good feeling
about this place.

07:03.028 --> 07:04.628
- Really?
- Especially the bedroom.

07:04.663 --> 07:06.697
I think we could get up
to some trouble in there--

07:06.731 --> 07:08.365
You've said that about
every place we've seen.

07:08.399 --> 07:09.433
Well, that's just a tribute

07:09.467 --> 07:11.335
to how warm I am for your form, woman.

07:11.369 --> 07:12.536
You know what?

07:12.571 --> 07:13.737
I'm still chafing
from this morning, so...

07:13.772 --> 07:15.472
I'm sorry.
Hotels make me horny.

07:15.507 --> 07:17.408
What doesn't make you horny, baby?

07:17.442 --> 07:19.710
Um... cockroaches.

07:19.744 --> 07:21.578
Dead babies.

07:21.613 --> 07:22.813
Poop.

07:22.847 --> 07:24.247
[Laughing] Shut up.

07:24.282 --> 07:25.582
Look how close we'd be to the beach.

07:25.616 --> 07:28.151
- And the homeless.
- Which would surely alleviate

07:28.185 --> 07:30.453
any homesickness for New York
that might develop.

07:30.488 --> 07:31.721
- [Groans]
- Oh, God.

07:31.756 --> 07:33.156
You so don't wanna do this, huh?

07:33.191 --> 07:35.358
You know what?
I just think of Becca.

07:35.393 --> 07:36.660
- Yeah?
- And I-I--

07:36.694 --> 07:38.328
and it--
it feels all wrong.

07:38.362 --> 07:40.130
But she's so little and adaptable.

07:40.164 --> 07:42.265
Not to mention
totally dependent on us.

07:42.300 --> 07:43.667
If she complained at all,

07:43.701 --> 07:45.335
we could easily threaten
to abandon her.

07:45.369 --> 07:48.071
I'm pretty sure that would
shut her up immediately.

07:48.105 --> 07:49.606
[Both laughing]

07:49.640 --> 07:51.908
You really sure about this?

07:51.942 --> 07:53.643
I'm not, no.
Not--not at all.

07:53.678 --> 07:55.278
- Jesus.
- Charlie thought it would be

07:55.313 --> 07:56.980
a good idea for me
to spend some time out here

07:57.014 --> 08:00.183
so people could put this
beautiful visage to the name.

08:00.217 --> 08:02.418
And I'm trying to do
what my agent says for once

08:02.453 --> 08:05.521
rather than just telling him
to fuck off and get me paid.

08:05.556 --> 08:06.656
You know what?

08:06.690 --> 08:08.257
Huh?

08:08.292 --> 08:09.659
We were doing just fine.

08:09.693 --> 08:11.694
- No, we weren't.
- Yes, we were, we were.

08:11.728 --> 08:13.796
We couldn't even afford cable, Karen.

08:13.830 --> 08:15.331
That was a choice.

08:15.365 --> 08:16.665
- Really?
- Yes.

08:16.699 --> 08:18.000
Whatever.

08:18.034 --> 08:21.736
You're not being
a very supportive baby mama.

08:21.770 --> 08:23.938
I thought I was your muse.

08:23.972 --> 08:26.073
You are.

08:26.108 --> 08:28.042
And right now, you're
inspiring me to point out that,

08:28.076 --> 08:30.444
compared to what we paid for
in New York for a broom closet,

08:30.478 --> 08:32.780
that place is a steal.

08:34.616 --> 08:35.849
- [Sighs]
- Plus, you'd get that.

08:35.884 --> 08:37.918
[Urine trickling]

08:37.953 --> 08:40.154
- [Laughing]
- Just like home.

08:41.523 --> 08:43.957
So next we have...

08:43.993 --> 08:45.861
We need to go to, um...

08:45.895 --> 08:47.762
- What is it, "Sepul-Veda"?
- Sepul-Veda?

08:47.797 --> 08:50.399
[Paper rustling]

08:50.433 --> 08:52.534
Look alive.

08:52.569 --> 08:54.103
Ah, sorry.

08:54.137 --> 08:56.039
Where'd you just go?

08:56.073 --> 08:57.140
Nowhere.

08:57.174 --> 08:59.376
Just digging deep.

08:59.410 --> 09:00.978
Okay...

09:01.012 --> 09:03.247
What rhymes with "vagina"?

09:03.281 --> 09:04.715
I'm not gonna
sing "vagina."

09:04.749 --> 09:06.116
Your loss--
that could be

09:06.150 --> 09:08.085
some seriously groundbreaking shit.

09:08.119 --> 09:10.086
Yeah, some songwriter you are.

09:10.121 --> 09:11.721
Ooh, ooh, ooh.
Here we go.

09:11.755 --> 09:13.255
Here we go.
I got something here.

09:13.290 --> 09:14.256
- You ready?
- Yep.

09:14.291 --> 09:16.325
People think it's funny.

09:16.359 --> 09:17.859
♪ But it's really hot and runny ♪

09:17.894 --> 09:19.194
♪ diarrhea ♪

09:19.228 --> 09:20.528
♪ diarrhea ♪

09:20.563 --> 09:21.629
