09:21.664 --> 09:23.064
But it's really good on toast.

09:23.099 --> 09:25.700
♪ Diarrhea, diarrhea ♪
Here comes the chorus.

09:25.734 --> 09:27.402
- ♪ Diarrhea, cha cha cha ♪
- Okay, asshole.

09:27.437 --> 09:29.037
Come on, come on, come on.
This is my career.

09:29.072 --> 09:30.339
You don't wanna have any fun?
No fun.

09:30.374 --> 09:31.674
Okay, no fun, no fun.

09:31.708 --> 09:32.775
All right, what do you
want to write about?

09:32.809 --> 09:36.245
[Sighs] I don't know.
I just...

09:36.280 --> 09:38.481
Well, tell me about
the guy you left behind.

09:38.516 --> 09:39.850
You know, that guy.
That one.

09:39.884 --> 09:42.386
Um...

09:42.420 --> 09:44.922
He was jealous.

09:44.956 --> 09:47.257
Well, you seem to attract
the jealous type.

09:47.291 --> 09:48.392
You bad girl, you.

09:48.426 --> 09:50.293
I'm not bad, I'm just...

09:50.328 --> 09:51.394
drawn that way.

09:51.428 --> 09:53.430
A hip-hop
Jessica Rabbit, huh?

09:53.464 --> 09:57.167
He didn't like...
the attention I was getting

09:57.201 --> 09:58.534
from our friend Samurai.

09:58.569 --> 10:00.036
Well, who could blame him?

10:00.070 --> 10:01.837
And that I got the offer to come here

10:01.871 --> 10:03.472
and to make a record.

10:03.506 --> 10:05.240
So...

10:07.977 --> 10:11.613
I... have
an offer for you!

10:11.648 --> 10:12.648
[Chuckles]

10:12.682 --> 10:13.816
Why are you yelling?

10:13.850 --> 10:14.951
It's my style.

10:14.985 --> 10:17.153
My thing.
It's--it's bombastic.

10:17.188 --> 10:18.321
My clients love it.

10:18.356 --> 10:19.689
Not this client.

10:19.724 --> 10:21.124
- Oh.
- Sorry.

10:21.159 --> 10:23.127
- [Chuckles]
- What's the offer?

10:23.161 --> 10:25.396
There is a script.
It's at Universal.

10:25.430 --> 10:26.764
They're about to start production.

10:26.798 --> 10:27.798
They need a polish.

10:27.832 --> 10:29.333
Oh!
I can polish things.

10:29.368 --> 10:30.434
- Ah.
- Yeah.

10:30.469 --> 10:32.837
You have never polished anything...

10:32.871 --> 10:34.038
- Karen...
- In your entire life, ever.

10:34.072 --> 10:35.939
Do I not polish
your beautiful lady parts

10:35.974 --> 10:37.708
on a semi-nightly basis?

10:37.742 --> 10:38.742
[High-pitched]
Nailed it!

10:38.776 --> 10:41.677
[Trills] How much?

10:41.712 --> 10:44.280
25 a week.

10:45.282 --> 10:46.248
25...

10:46.282 --> 10:48.450
grand.

10:48.485 --> 10:50.519
- Look at his face.
- I love L.A.

10:50.553 --> 10:52.187
- [Laughs]
- I love it! I love it.

10:52.221 --> 10:53.655
I said it, I meant it.

10:53.689 --> 10:54.956
I'm here to represent it.

10:54.991 --> 10:56.458
- You know that.
- Who are you right now?

10:56.492 --> 10:57.759
I don't know.
I don't know.

10:57.793 --> 10:58.994
Whoo!

10:59.028 --> 11:00.862
You're gonna love it here
too, Karenina.

11:00.896 --> 11:01.896
They kissed.

11:01.931 --> 11:03.498
I'm telling you--
ooh, ooh.

11:03.532 --> 11:05.166
I don't think that...

11:05.201 --> 11:06.701
a decision has yet been made.

11:06.735 --> 11:08.837
- Why?
- Well, because, you know,

11:08.871 --> 11:10.271
we're still looking at places.

11:10.305 --> 11:11.505
Uh, "we" means "she."

11:11.539 --> 11:13.807
- I sensed that.
- Yeah.

11:13.842 --> 11:14.808
You know what?

11:14.843 --> 11:16.243
This motherfucker had to drag me

11:16.278 --> 11:17.745
kicking and screaming here.

11:17.779 --> 11:19.079
At first, I hated it.

11:19.114 --> 11:21.381
Now I fucking love it.

11:21.416 --> 11:22.749
Okay, what do you love about it?

11:22.784 --> 11:24.618
Everything is fucking fake!

11:24.652 --> 11:26.487
Okay? The houses
are like sets,

11:26.521 --> 11:28.789
and the people are
indistinguishable from actors.

11:28.823 --> 11:29.991
It's awesome.

11:30.025 --> 11:33.028
Hank's career
is about to explode, Karen.

11:33.062 --> 11:34.629
He needs to be here.

11:34.664 --> 11:35.630
Charlie Runkle.

11:35.665 --> 11:38.333
Ah, Ali, so nice to see you.

11:38.367 --> 11:39.801
You too, mwah.
Mwah.

11:39.836 --> 11:42.437
Mwah.
Is this him?

11:42.471 --> 11:44.573
Hank Moody, Ali Andrews,

11:44.607 --> 11:46.441
your executive on <i>God Hates Us All.</i>

11:46.475 --> 11:47.642
Ah, nice to meet you.

11:47.676 --> 11:49.043
You didn't tell me he was gorgeous.

11:49.077 --> 11:50.745
Well, for you to discover.

11:50.779 --> 11:52.613
It's great to finally meet you, Hank.

11:52.648 --> 11:54.382
- I'm a huge fan.
- No, you're not.

11:54.416 --> 11:56.184
[Laughs] Oh, I'm not, huh?

11:56.218 --> 11:58.686
I am a huge fan, Hank.
I swear.

11:58.720 --> 12:00.588
